msgid "CameraFollowCursorCV"
msgstr "CameraFollowCursorCV"

#: ../../mainclass.rst:4
msgid ""
"``CameraFollowCursorCV`` is the primary class for creating code typing "
"animation videos. It handles code parsing, syntax highlighting, camera "
"movement, and the full rendering pipeline."
msgstr "``CameraFollowCursorCV`` 是用于创建代码输入动画视频的主类。它处理代码解析、语法高亮、相机移动和完整的渲染流水线。"

