#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:1 of
msgid ""
"CameraFollowCursorCV is a class designed to create animated videos that "
"simulate the process of typing code. It animates code line by line and "
"character by character while smoothly moving the camera to follow the "
"cursor, creating a professional-looking coding demonstration."
msgstr ""
"CameraFollowCursorCV "
"是一个用于创建模拟打字过程的动画视频的类。它逐行逐字符地动画化代码，同时平滑移动镜头跟随光标，打造出专业的代码演示效果。"

#: ../../mainclass.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:4 of
msgid ""
"The code to be animated. **When using a string**, provide a tuple with the "
"first element as ``'string'`` and the second element as the code string. "
"**When using a file**, provide a tuple with the first element as ``'file'`` "
"and the second element as the file path."
msgstr ""
"要动画化的代码。**使用字符串时**，提供一个元组，第一个元素为 "
"``'string'``，第二个元素为代码字符串。**使用文件时**，提供一个元组，第一个元素为 ``'file'``，第二个元素为文件路径。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:6 of
msgid "The programming language of the code."
msgstr "代码的编程语言。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:8 of
msgid "The style for syntax highlighting. Defaults to ``\"material\"``."
msgstr "语法高亮的样式。默认为 ``\"material\"``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:10 of
msgid ""
"The line spacing for the code. Defaults to :data:`~.DEFAULT_LINE_SPACING`."
msgstr "代码的行间距。默认为 :data:`~.DEFAULT_LINE_SPACING`。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:12 of
msgid ""
"The range of typing intervals between characters. Defaults to "
"(:data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`, :data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`)."
msgstr ""
"字符之间的打字间隔范围。默认为 (:data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`, "
":data:`~.DEFAULT_TYPE_INTERVAL`)。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:14 of
msgid "The scale factor for the camera. Defaults to 0.5."
msgstr "相机的缩放因子。默认为 0.5。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:16 of
msgid ""
"The name of the output video file. Defaults to ``\"CameraFollowCursorCV\"``."
msgstr "输出视频文件的名称。默认为 ``\"CameraFollowCursorCV\"``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV:18 of
msgid "The renderer to use for video rendering. Defaults to ``'cairo'``."
msgstr "用于视频渲染的渲染器。默认为 ``'cairo'``。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV._create_scene:1 of
msgid "Create manim scene to animate code rendering."
msgstr "创建 manim 场景以动画化代码渲染。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:1 of
msgid "Render the animated code video."
msgstr "渲染动画代码视频。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:3 of
msgid "This method triggers the full rendering pipeline:"
msgstr "此方法触发完整的渲染流水线："

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:5 of
msgid ""
"**Manim rendering** – the code typing animation is rendered using the "
"configured backend (Cairo or OpenGL)."
msgstr "**Manim 渲染** – 使用配置的后端（Cairo 或 OpenGL）渲染代码输入动画。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:6 of
msgid ""
"**Glow effect** – a soft glow post-processing effect is applied to the raw "
"video via MoviePy."
msgstr "**柔光效果** – 通过 MoviePy 对原始视频应用柔光后期处理效果。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:8 of
msgid ""
"The final video file is saved next to Manim's default output path with the "
"name specified by ``video_name``."
msgstr "最终视频文件保存在 Manim 默认输出路径旁，文件名由 ``video_name`` 指定。"

#: CodeVideoRenderer.renderer.CameraFollowCursorCV.render:10 of
msgid ""
"Whether to print progress messages and timing logs to the console during "
"rendering. Defaults to :data:`~.DEFAULT_OUTPUT_VALUE`."
msgstr "是否在渲染期间向控制台打印进度消息和计时日志。默认值为 :data:`~.DEFAULT_OUTPUT_VALUE`。"

