msgid ""
"The final MP4 file is typically located at "
"``./media/videos/1080p60/{video_name}.mp4`` (the exact sub-directory depends"
" on Manim's quality configuration)."
msgstr ""
"最终的 MP4 文件通常位于 ``./media/videos/1080p60/{video_name}.mp4``\\ （具体的子目录取决于 "
"Manim 的质量配置）。"

